{"id":"aba3e7b663e69b784af01852cdfdff2cf12f70f5","axis":"silent","repo":"payloadcms/payload","sha":"aba3e7b663e69b784af01852cdfdff2cf12f70f5","parsed":{"files":[{"path":"docs/admin/admin-panel-location.mdx","lines":["@@ -265,6 +265,26 @@ The import map is **never regenerated** during:","   map automatically."," </Banner>"," ","+### Generating the Import Map on build","+","+Running `payload build` generates the Import Map (and your TypeScript types) and","+then runs `next build`. Because the Import Map is statically imported at compile","+time, generating it _before_ `next build` ensures your production build always","+bundles an up-to-date Import Map.","+","+The Payload templates seed this for you:","+","+```json","+{","+  \"scripts\": {","+    \"build\": \"payload build\"","+  }","+}","+```","+","+`payload build` forwards any extra arguments to `next build` (e.g. `payload build --turbopack`).","+Pass `--no-types` to skip type generation (`payload build --no-types`).","+"," ## Troubleshooting"," "," ### Import map not found error"],"additions":20,"deletions":0,"truncated":false},{"path":"examples/astro/payload/package.json","lines":["@@ -12,7 +12,7 @@","     }","   },","   \"scripts\": {","-    \"build\": \"next build\",","+    \"build\": \"payload build\",","     \"dev\": \"next dev --turbo\",","     \"devsafe\": \"rm -rf .next && next dev\",","     \"generate:importmap\": \"payload generate:importmap\","],"additions":1,"deletions":1,"truncated":false},{"path":"examples/auth/package.json","lines":["@@ -6,7 +6,7 @@","   \"type\": \"module\",","   \"main\": \"dist/server.js\",","   \"scripts\": {","-    \"build\": \"cross-env NODE_OPTIONS=--no-deprecation next build\",","+    \"build\": \"cross-env NODE_OPTIONS=--no-deprecation payload build\",","     \"dev\": \"cross-env NODE_OPTIONS=--no-deprecation && pnpm seed && next dev\",","     \"generate:importmap\": \"cross-env NODE_OPTIONS=--no-deprecation payload generate:importmap\",","     \"generate:schema\": \"payload